WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.120
It is a tempting assumption that an AWS rep will

00:00:03.120 --> 00:00:06.240
automatically help you. The reality is you must sell to

00:00:06.240 --> 00:00:09.360
them first. AppsFlyer is software, so it does not immediately

00:00:09.360 --> 00:00:12.480
increase cloud spend. You must prove how it will scale

00:00:12.480 --> 00:00:15.600
their account later.
